{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/pinkmosphere-saat-adiknya-rika-si-preman-sekolah-jatuh-cinta/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Pinkmosphere: Saat Adiknya Rika si Preman Sekolah Jatuh Cinta","content":"\n<p>Masih ingat nggak sama Edo? Adiknya Rika dari komik Rika si Preman Sekolah ini beberapa kali muncul di komiknya sang kakak. Anak SD yang satu ini, walaupun kelihatan polos sebenarnya cukup pintar loh. Buktinya aja di komik spinoff Pinkmosphere, Edo ternyata bisa masuk ke SMP 13 yang jadi salah satu SMP cluster tertinggi. Di kelasnya, Edo jadi yang paling pintar dan dia nggak ragu untuk menyombongkannya ke semua orang, termasuk teman baiknya Atmaja dan rival semasa SD Icha.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53691\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/pinkmosphere-saat-adiknya-rika-si-preman-sekolah-jatuh-cinta/attachment/01-pinkmosphere/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-pinkmosphere.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-pinkmosphere\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-pinkmosphere-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-pinkmosphere.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-pinkmosphere.jpg\" alt=\"Edo melihat Suzakura untuk pertama kalinya. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53691\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-pinkmosphere.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-pinkmosphere-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Edo melihat Suzakura untuk pertama kalinya. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Di usia seumurannya, Edo tentunya menjalani berbagai hal\nbaru yang menimbulkan perasaan yang belum pernah ia tahu. Salah satunya adalah\ncinta! Di satu siang, Edo melihat seorang siswi dari SMA St. Cassimier yang\ntengah bermain basket. Berbagai perasaan berkecamuk dalam diri Edo. Meski malu,\nEdo memberanikan diri untuk berkenalan dengannya. Namanya adalah Suzakura,\norang Jepang yang besar di Indonesia.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53692\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/pinkmosphere-saat-adiknya-rika-si-preman-sekolah-jatuh-cinta/attachment/02-pinkmosphere/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-pinkmosphere.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-pinkmosphere\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-pinkmosphere-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-pinkmosphere.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-pinkmosphere.jpg\" alt=\"Edo mencoba pendekatan. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53692\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-pinkmosphere.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-pinkmosphere-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Edo mencoba pendekatan. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Meski belum punya pengalaman pacaran, Edo berusaha untuk\nbisa lebih dekat dengan Suzakura, sampai-sampai mendatangi sekolahnya yang\nbertetangga dengan SMP Edo. Ia memberanikan diri untuk mencoba berbagai hal\nyang belum pernah ia lakukan sebelumnya, segalanya agar lebih dekat dengan Suzakura.\nNamun, siapkah Edo untuk mengetahui kehidupan senpai-nya yang misterius itu?</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53693\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/pinkmosphere-saat-adiknya-rika-si-preman-sekolah-jatuh-cinta/attachment/03-pinkmosphere/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-pinkmosphere.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-pinkmosphere\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-pinkmosphere-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-pinkmosphere.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-pinkmosphere.jpg\" alt=\"Pinkmosphere sajikan dinamika romantis Edo dan Suzakura. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53693\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-pinkmosphere.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-pinkmosphere-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Pinkmosphere sajikan dinamika romantis Edo dan Suzakura. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Komik spinoff Rika si Preman Sekolah, Pinkmosphere, juga digambar oleh komikusnya Rika, FairyDemon. Komikus yang akrab disapa Mang Nono ini juga dibantu oleh Yukimpoi untuk ilustrasi background serta pewarnaannya. Berbeda dengan komik Rika, Pinkmosphere merupakan komik yang condong ke elemen drama dan romance. Momen boy meets girl yang dialami Edo dan Suzakura, serta perbedaan status dan usia, merupakan setup yang oke banget buat sebuah cerita romance yang menarik.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: </strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/rika-si-preman-sekolah-siap-menghancurkan-masa-indahmu/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Rika&nbsp;si&nbsp;Preman&nbsp;Sekolah&nbsp;Siap&nbsp;Menghancurkan&nbsp;Masa&nbsp;Indahmu!</strong></a></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53694\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/pinkmosphere-saat-adiknya-rika-si-preman-sekolah-jatuh-cinta/attachment/04-pinkmosphere/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-pinkmosphere.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-pinkmosphere\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-pinkmosphere-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-pinkmosphere.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-pinkmosphere.jpg\" alt=\"Bukan spinoffnya Rika kalau belum ada dialog bahasa Sunda. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53694\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-pinkmosphere.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-pinkmosphere-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Bukan spinoffnya Rika kalau belum ada dialog bahasa Sunda. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Meski demikian, humor-humor khas Rika masih bisa kamu\ntemukan di sini. Memang agak sedikit jinak sih, tapi berbagai dialog lucu yang\ndilontarkan Edo dan Atmaja dalam bahasa Sunda pasti bisa bikin kamu ketawa. Oh\nya, karena komik Pinkmosphere punya setting yang sama dengan komik Rika, bakal\nada beberapa cameo dari komik tersebut. Bisakah kamu temukan siapa saja mereka?</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53695\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/pinkmosphere-saat-adiknya-rika-si-preman-sekolah-jatuh-cinta/attachment/05-pinkmosphere/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-pinkmosphere.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quo